title: 08/19/2021 DPS Hour 3 Jordan Love Unlikely to Play Vs the Jets
itunes:title: 08/19/2021 DPS Hour 3 Jordan Love Unlikely to Play Vs the Jets
description:
Jonas Knox, Brady Quinn and LaVar Arrington, in for Dan, react to Jordan Love likely missing week 2 of the preseason and how that adds tension between Aaron Rodgers and the Packers. The guys read between the lines and think Tom Brady was miffed about the Titans picking Ryan Tannehill over him last offseason. Plus, some news about NIL, the Washington Football Team's new name and the Saints season-ticket policy on The Scraps.
